  <div>
   <p xml:id="1" begin="00:00:00.217" end="00:00:01.384">TIME LIKE TONIGHT TO GET A</p>
   <p xml:id="2" begin="00:00:01.151" end="00:00:02.953">COUPLE IN.</p>
   <p xml:id="3" begin="00:00:01.518" end="00:00:08.725">SO DON'T GET MAD AT ME IF I</p>
   <p xml:id="4" begin="00:00:03.086" end="00:00:10.760">CAN'T GET TO IT.</p>
   <p xml:id="5" begin="00:00:08.859" end="00:00:11.328">THE &quot;TIP OF THE DAY,&quot; HERE'S MY</p>
   <p xml:id="6" begin="00:00:10.894" end="00:00:13.363">SUGGESTION.</p>
   <p xml:id="7" begin="00:00:11.461" end="00:00:18.635">EVERY AMERICAN SHOULD DISPLAY</p>
   <p xml:id="8" begin="00:00:13.497" end="00:00:22.105">THE FLAG.</p>
   <p xml:id="9" begin="00:00:18.768" end="00:00:23.073">THAT SHOWS PATRIOTISM.</p>
   <p xml:id="10" begin="00:00:22.239" end="00:00:29.246">BUT IT ALSO DEVASTATES THAT WE,</p>
   <p xml:id="11" begin="00:00:23.206" end="00:00:31.214">THE AMERICAN PEOPLE, ON A GOOD</p>
   <p xml:id="12" begin="00:00:29.379" end="00:00:32.682">RACE RELATIONS.</p>
   <p xml:id="13" begin="00:00:31.348" end="00:00:33.550">HE DID AMAZING THINGS IN HIS</p>
   <p xml:id="14" begin="00:00:32.816" end="00:00:35.519">SHORT LIFE SPAN.</p>
   <p xml:id="15" begin="00:00:33.684" end="00:00:37.187">HE WAS NONVIOLENT, BRILLIANT,</p>
   <p xml:id="16" begin="00:00:35.652" end="00:00:39.156">AND HE DESERVES TO BE HONORED.</p>
   <p xml:id="17" begin="00:00:37.321" end="00:00:40.724">SO AGAIN, THE TIP, GET A FLAG,</p>
   <p xml:id="18" begin="00:00:39.289" end="00:00:42.426">PUT IT UP ON MONDAY.</p>
  </div>
